{"tid":2301977,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"因應香港人質素下降 本 HR 決定跟隨政府決定","createTime":"2020-11-26T18:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T00:23:42.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50f70c16c891f9b93c6cce31510d2b25bb6cad41","tid":2301977,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"今朝同大老細 propose 咗新請人策略 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/mouse2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-&gt; Cut HK local fg headcount, 增加大陸 headcount ，比起香港學生更有關係，又勤力 (UST non local&gt; UST local)<br />\n<br />\n-&gt; HK office 傾向請大陸大學生，將本地三大降至 second tier 考慮 (清北&gt;三大)<br />\n<br />\n-&gt; 提高 MT program 對 local 嘅 gpa 要求，cgpa 須達  3.6/4.0，不得其中一個 sem 少於 3.5 ，必須提交2年內 ielts + 武肺測試結果 + 良民證"},{"pid":"c2aa72c076db5519ba20e44cd2306aee1aa0fd2a","tid":2301977,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f5e607a20738214d1f88cd7eab4402932b9956a","tid":2301977,"uid":29836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蝌大狗冇工開<br />\n慘"},{"pid":"2aae3e6ae6c5c516334b2080d0cbeb8fe79a4b1e","tid":2301977,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"政府公布，「優才計劃」配額由每年一千名增加至二千名。<br />\n<br />\n政府說，自2018年8月公布首份「人才清單」後，「優才計劃」申請顯著上升，獲推薦分配名額的申請人，由2017年的411名，增加至2019年874名，雖然未達到每年1千名的配額，<strong>但政府決定增加至每年配額2千名，以擴充香港的人才庫，加強香港作為亞洲國際都會的地位。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%87-%E5%84%AA%E6%89%8D%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D%E7%94%B1%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4-%E5%8D%83%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%83%E5%90%8D-082328232.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%2